    "Sculpture henceforth became his main topic of research and writing.": [],
    "He was appointed Deputy Keeper of the Department in 1958.": [],
    "A 1960 introduction to the Museum's collection of Hispano-Moresque carvings, <em>Caskets from Cordoba</em> was notable.": [
        [
            50,
            66,
            [
                "Hispano-Mosque"
            ]
